  )# Pinnacle News

A modern online newspaper built with Next.js.

## Features
- Breaking News ticker (top bar)
- Headline story section
- Grid of latest stories
- Sidebar with categories + trending
- Sample placeholder articles

## How to Run
1. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   npm install
   ```
2. Start development server:
   ```bash
   npm run dev
   ```
3. Build for production:
   ```bash
   npm run build
   npm start
   ```

## Adding Articles
- Create new files in `pages/articles/` (e.g., `article1.js`).
- Each file represents one news story.
- Update the homepage (`pages/index.js`) to include your new articles.

## Deployment
1. Push this project to your GitHub repo `pinnacle-news`.
2. Connect repo to [Vercel](https://vercel.com).
3. Click **Deploy** â†’ Your site goes live!
